Title: Nascar Racing 2002 Season
Genre: racing / simulation / sports
Released: 14th February 2002
Developer: Papyrus Design Group
Publisher: Sierra Entertainment
Description:
Race Against Jeff Gordon, Kevin Harvick, Dale Earnhardt Jr., Dale Jarrett, and more in the 2002 Season! Get behind the wheel of a 750 horsepower stock car and battle for the championship on real-life tracks. Get under the hood to fine-tune your car or just jump in and race against the best in Arcade Mode. Feel the cars' vibrations, hear the roar of the engines, and sweat it out racing fender to fender at 180 miles per hour.

Bonus content: manual.

How to play:
1) Download the game;
2) Mount or burn disc image NR2002.iso;
3) Run SETUP.EXE to install the game (you will have to enter serial number, check key.txt);
4) After installation is complete, run nascar2002_update_1102.exe to patch the game;
5) After patching is complete, extract Crack.zip archive to game folder (overwrite original file);
6) Play the game without the disc.

If you like the game, SUPPORT the producers!
